items.description:
Stream/download: https://orcd.co/meetherattheloveparade

Smash The House honchos Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike join forces with the prominent Dutch DJ and Producer Maddix to put a new age spin on an unmistakable classic rave anthem. Featuring the vocal sounds of the exemplary Kiki Solvej, the trio of acts have injected Da Hool‚Äôs 1997 ‚ÄòMeet Her At The Love Parade‚Äô with an infectious techno-trance style that gives the timeless track an exciting new revamp.

The new track is a raver‚Äôs delight that combines elements of techno with its heavy fist-pumping kick beat and the high-paced cluster of hats and claps with trance-like synths and acid-heavy basslines. Sirens pierce through the beat creating moments of intensity and amplifying the build-ups. Kiki‚Äôs echoing voice can be heard throughout as it harmonizes with the track vocalizing lyrics in her native German tongue to add a layer of shade and mystery to the composition. 

Paying homage to one of dance music's most celebrated works, the original sample from Da Hool‚Äôs ‚ÄòMeet Her At The Love Parade‚Äô is featured periodically throughout the track. The catchy synth loop is a familiar pattern that brings nostalgia to listeners around the globe. Now, this dancefloor classic has a new burst of energy, courtesy of some of modern dance music‚Äôs biggest players.
